SUMMARY:Open Mic and Music Trivia
DESCRIPTION:Join us for the fifth Open Mic of 2026 in Davis. Last month we introduced a new Music Trivia contest throughout the evening to rave reviews!!! We will once again be including 4 rounds of 5 music-related questions as part of this month’s open mic. The winner will receive a $20 Watermelon Music gift card! \nWhether you’re looking for a venue to share your own talents or just looking to enjoy hearing (and seeing) some local performers\, we invite you to this free monthly event. We provide the sound\, stage and lights – the rest is up to you. Play us your favorite song\, tell us some jokes\, act out a scene from your favorite play with friends. \nWe ask only that each performance be suitable for an all-ages venue\, and that you arrive on time and stay until the end to support your fellow performers. \nFREE!!!\nDoors open/sign-ups @ 5:30.\nFirst act @ 6:00. \nWe hope to see you there!
URL:https://visitdavis.org/event/open-mic-and-music-trivia/
LOCATION:Watermelon Music\, 1970 Lake Blvd\, DAVIS\, CA\, 95616\, United States
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://visitdavis.org/wp-content/uploads/May2026_Open-Mic-1-Uksir2.jpg
ORGANIZER;CN="Watermelon Music":MAILTO:info@watermelonmusic.com
END:VEVENT
